---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Adults – Cara Colgate, LICSW" currentPage="adults">
  <div class="page-intro">
    <img
      src="/images/adults-stones.jpg"
      alt="Stacked stones balanced on a rock by the ocean"
      class="page-image"
    />
    <div class="intro-text">
      <p>
        Are you feeling like there is more to life? Do you wish relationships were more fulfilling
        or something would change? Is there more frustration in work or school than feelings of
        success? Do you wonder why parenting is so hard and how to find more joy and connection
        with your children?
      </p>
      <p>
        People come into therapy for many reasons. Whether your challenges seem big or small, they
        are worthy of consideration and support. With full commitment, therapy can help you find
        relief from negative feelings and increased fulfillment in life.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p>
    In my 20 years as a psychotherapist, I have worked with a wide range of clients, including
    professionals, parents, young adults, couples and seniors. I have experience helping
    individuals and families work through loss and grief, from supporting people who have suffered
    the death of a loved one to victims of life-changing accidents to divorcing parents struggling
    to find peace and support their children. I focus on communications and relationships, helping
    my clients increase their awareness of their own needs and learn to effectively communicate
    with those closest to them.
  </p>

  <p>
    The key to success in therapy is you. I can provide you with tools and support, but it is your
    desire and courage that make change happen. You are worth the investment. Challenges come
    everyone's way. Face yours with full support.{' '}
    <a href="/connect/">Contact me</a> today to get started.
  </p>
</Base>

<style>
  .page-intro {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 220px 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .intro-text p {
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  .page-image {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 4px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
  }

  p {
    margin-bottom: 1.3rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .page-intro {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .page-image {
      max-width: 260px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  }
</style>
